---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FidoNext — Privacy Policy">
	<main class="policy">
		<section>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="policy-updated">Last updated: February 2025</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>What We Collect</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Contact data you intentionally share with us (name, email, GitHub handle).</li>
				<li>Optional profile info when you apply to join the project.</li>
				<li>Basic operational metadata from our website (device + browser) used solely to prevent abuse.</li>
				<li>We do not collect message content or mesh traffic; everything stays end-to-end encrypted.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>How We Use Information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Responding to support requests or contributor applications.</li>
				<li>Sending project updates only if you explicitly opt in.</li>
				<li>Analyzing anonymous website traffic to improve onboarding.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Security & Storage</h2>
			<p>All sensitive data is stored with zero-knowledge encryption. Access is restricted to a minimal operations crew bound by confidentiality. We do not run third-party analytics or advertising trackers.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Your Rights</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Request a copy of the data you shared with us.</li>
				<li>Ask us to delete your contact information.</li>
				<li>Opt out of project communications at any time.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:dev@fidonext.org">dev@fidonext.org</a>.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Third Parties & Infrastructure</h2>
			<p>We rely on standard hosting and CDN providers. They do not have access to encrypted mesh content. Open-source licenses governing our codebase are published on <a href="https://github.com/fidonext" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>If we update this policy, we will revise the “Last updated” date and highlight changes in our repository.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>Questions? Reach us at <a href="mailto:dev@fidonext.org">dev@fidonext.org</a>.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

